It says, "keep out."

18
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:06,190
Well, they couldn't mean us,
Paradise.

19
00:01:06,190 --> 00:01:07,440
Where could it lead, I wonder?

20
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,190
Wait!

21
